1. *Pišeš* li često pisma svojim prijateljima? (Do you often *write* letters to your friends?)
2. Kada *pišeš* esej, važno je da budeš jasan i koncizan. (When you *write* an essay, it's important to be clear and concise.)
3. Ja sam već *pisao* ovaj sastav juče. (I already *wrote* this composition yesterday.)
4. Oni *pišu* knjigu o svom putovanju po Aziji. (They are *writing* a book about their journey through Asia.)
5. Da li si primetio da *pišu* novi mural na zidu zgrade? (Did you notice they are *painting* a new mural on the wall of the building?)
6. *Napisao* sam ti pismo, a ti si mi odgovorio e-mailom. (I *wrote* you a letter, and you replied to me by email.) 
7. Molim te, *napiši* svoje ime na ovoj listi. (Please *write* your name on this list.)
8. Ja *napisah* pismo, ali ga još nisam poslao. (I *wrote* a letter, but I haven't sent it yet.)
9. *Napisao* si izuzetno zanimljiv sastav. (You *wrote* an extremely interesting composition.)
10. Ne mogu da verujem da si *nacrtao* ovaj crtež, *pišeš* kao umetnik! (I can't believe you *drew* this drawing, you *write* like an artist!)